## ðŸŽ¯ **Fitur Lengkap Tema:**

### **âœ… Framework & Libraries:**
- Bootstrap 5.3.0
- Font Awesome 6.0.0
- Google Fonts (Inter)
- Responsive Design

### **âœ… Components:**
- Fixed Navigation dengan Search
- Hero Section
- Sidebar dengan Widgets
- Card-based Layout
- Modal Gallery
- Pagination
- Breadcrumbs

### **âœ… Post Features:**
- Views Counter Integration
- Reading Time Calculator
- Image Overflow Protection
- Social Sharing
- Comments System
- Featured/Banner Badges
- Category Links
- SEO Meta Tags

### **âœ… Pages Include:**
- Homepage dengan Hero
- Post Detail dengan Comments
- Gallery & Gallery Detail
- Category Posts
- Search dengan Suggestions
- Static Pages
- Responsive Sidebar

### **âœ… Color Scheme:**
- Primary: #ffc107 (Orange)
- Secondary: #ff8800 (Dark Orange)
- Konsisten dengan Brand Dinkes

## ðŸ“¥ **Cara Install:**
1. Extract file ZIP ke folder `resources/views/themes/`
2. Update config untuk menggunakan tema `dinkes-theme`
3. Pastikan route dan model sudah sesuai
4. Upload logo dan gambar hero ke folder `public/assets/`

Tema ini siap digunakan dan sudah include semua fitur yang kita kembangkan sebelumnya! ðŸš€    .post-content table {
        width: 100% !important;
        max-width: 100% !important;
        table-layout: auto !important;
        overflow-x: auto;
        display: block;
        white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .post-content iframe,
    .post-content video,
    .post-content embed,
    .post-content object {
        max-width: 100% !important;
        width: 100% !important;
        height: auto !important;
    }

    /* Article Enhancement */
    .article-card {
        border-radius: 15px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .article-image {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        height: 400px;
    }

    .article-image img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .article-image:hover img {
